{"comments":"BlurSigma - Gaussian blur standard deviation.\n\nSigma (σ) is the standard deviation parameter for Gaussian blur.\nIt controls the width of the blur kernel more precisely than radius.\n\nRange: 0 to finite (clamps at 0, no upper bound but must remain finite)\n- **0**: No blur (sharp)\n- **1.0**: Subtle blur\n- **5.0**: Moderate blur\n- **10.0+**: Heavy blur\n\nRelationship to radius: radius ≈ 2 * sigma (approximate)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","BlurSigma"],"BlurSigma"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[50,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BlurSigma.purs","start":[50,1]},"title":"eqBlurSigma"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","BlurSigma"],"BlurSigma"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[51,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BlurSigma.purs","start":[51,1]},"title":"ordBlurSigma"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","BlurSigma"],"BlurSigma"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[54,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BlurSigma.purs","start":[53,1]},"title":"showBlurSigma"}],"comments":"Blur sigma (standard deviation) for Gaussian blur (0 to finite)\n\nRepresents the mathematical sigma parameter in the Gaussian function.\nMore precise control than blur radius for algorithmic blur.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[48,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BlurSigma.purs","start":[48,1]},"title":"BlurSigma"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a blur sigma, clamping to 0 minimum and ensuring finite\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","BlurSigma"],"BlurSigma"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[61,33],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BlurSigma.purs","start":[61,1]},"title":"blurSigma"},{"children":[],"comments":"Extract the raw Number value\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","BlurSigma"],"BlurSigma"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[89,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/BlurSigma.purs","start":[89,1]},"title":"unwrap"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert to Number (passthrough for this type)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Surface","BlurSigma"],"BlurSigma"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[93,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Surface/B